content:
Calculate my age if I provide my date of birth in the format DD/MM/YYYY, such as '28/02/1997'?
Begin!

I apologize, but I cannot find a function specifically designed to calculate age from a date of birth among the available tools for SQUAKE. The provided tools seem to be related to carbon emissions calculation and sustainable product building, which do not include age calculation functionality.

Since I cannot use the existing tools to solve this task, I will use the Finish function to explain the situation.
